<div class="swiper border">
  <div class="swiper-wrapper text-center my-5">
    <div class="swiper-slide">
      <p class="fs-3">ボタンを押して<br />さっそくチェック！</p>
      <p>説明が見たい人は<br />スライドをめくろう！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="swiper-slide">
      <p class="fs-3">どんなサービス？</p>
      <p>身の回りのモノを写真に撮るだけで<br />呪物かどうかチェックできるぞ！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="swiper-slide">
      <p class="fs-3">呪物ってなに？</p>
      <p>人間の理解を超えた<br />呪いの力をもつモノのことだ！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="swiper-slide">
      <p class="fs-3">呪物は良くないモノ？</p>
      <p>人に幸せをもたらすモノもあるぞ！<br />神社のお守りや御札がそうだな！</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
  <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
  <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
  <div class="swiper-scrollbar"></div>
</div>
<div class="mt-5">
  <%= form_with url: result_path do |f| %>
    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.file_field :upload_image, onchange: 'previewImage()', accept: 'image/*', class: 'form-control' %>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group text-center">
      <%= f.submit 'チェックする', class: 'btn btn-danger mt-3' %>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <%= image_tag '', id: 'preview', class: 'profile-image mt-3', width: '300' %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<%= javascript_pack_tag "swiper" %>

<script>
  function previewImage() {
  const target = this.event.target;
  const file = target.files[0];
  const reader  = new FileReader();
  reader.onloadend = function () {
      const preview = document.querySelector("#preview")
      if(preview) {
        preview.src = reader.result;
      }
    }
    if (file) {
        reader.readAsDataURL(file);
    }
  }
</script>
